---
// FAQ.astro - QIFESS FAQ Section Component
---

<section class="faq">
  <div class="faq-container" id="faq">
    <div class="faq-header">
      <h2 class="section-title fade-in">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle fade-in delay-1">
        Get answers to common questions about QIFESS Field Service Management
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="faq-content">
      <div class="faq-item fade-in delay-2">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>What is QIFESS and how does it work?</span>
          <svg
            class="faq-icon"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
          >
            <polyline points="6,9 12,15 18,9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="faq-answer-content">
            <p>
              QIFESS (Qualita Indonesia Field Service System) is a comprehensive field service
              management solution. The system enables companies to manage field operations in
              real-time with features including technician tracking, automated scheduling, work
              order management, and deep analytics to improve operational efficiency.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item fade-in delay-3">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>Is QIFESS suitable for small and medium-sized businesses?</span>
          <svg
            class="faq-icon"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
          >
            <polyline points="6,9 12,15 18,9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="faq-answer-content">
            <p>
              Yes, QIFESS is designed to be scalable and flexible. Whether you're an SME with 5-10
              technicians or a large company with hundreds of field technicians, the system can be
              customized to meet your business needs and budget with various service packages
              available.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item fade-in delay-4">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>How does the real-time tracking system work in QIFESS?</span>
          <svg
            class="faq-icon"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
          >
            <polyline points="6,9 12,15 18,9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="faq-answer-content">
            <p>
              QIFESS uses GPS technology and a mobile app to track technician locations in
              real-time. Managers can view team positions, job status, and estimated completion
              times. Technicians can check-in/check-out, update progress, and send reports directly
              from the field through the mobile application.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item fade-in delay-5">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>Is company data secure in the QIFESS system?</span>
          <svg
            class="faq-icon"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
          >
            <polyline points="6,9 12,15 18,9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="faq-answer-content">
            <p>
              Data security is our top priority. QIFESS uses 256-bit SSL encryption, daily automatic
              backups, secure cloud servers, and has ISO 27001 certification. All customer data is
              stored in certified data centers in Indonesia with compliance to data protection
              regulations.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item fade-in delay-6">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>How long does QIFESS implementation take?</span>
          <svg
            class="faq-icon"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
          >
            <polyline points="6,9 12,15 18,9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="faq-answer-content">
            <p>
              QIFESS implementation can be completed in 2-4 weeks depending on business complexity.
              The process includes: initial consultation (1-2 days), system setup (3-5 days), data
              migration (2-3 days), team training (2-3 days), and go-live with full support. Our
              support team will assist during the transition period.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item fade-in delay-7">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>Can QIFESS be integrated with existing systems?</span>
          <svg
            class="faq-icon"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
          >
            <polyline points="6,9 12,15 18,9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="faq-answer-content">
            <p>
              Yes, QIFESS has robust APIs for integration with various systems such as ERP, CRM,
              accounting software, and inventory systems. We also provide specialized connectors for
              popular software like SAP, Odoo, and Accurate. Our technical team will assist with the
              integration process.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item fade-in delay-8">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>What is QIFESS's pricing model?</span>
          <svg
            class="faq-icon"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
          >
            <polyline points="6,9 12,15 18,9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="faq-answer-content">
            <p>
              QIFESS offers flexible pricing plans tailored to your business needs. We provide
              detailed pricing information during our consultation process to ensure you get the
              best value for your investment. Start with our free trial to experience the full
              system capabilities before making any commitment.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item fade-in delay-9">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>Are training and support available?</span>
          <svg
            class="faq-icon"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
          >
            <polyline points="6,9 12,15 18,9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="faq-answer-content">
            <p>
              QIFESS support team is available 24/7 through phone, email, and live chat. We provide
              comprehensive training for admins and users, complete documentation, video tutorials,
              and regular webinars. Enterprise clients also get dedicated customer success managers
              and access to our user community forum.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="faq-item fade-in delay-10">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>Can I try QIFESS before subscribing?</span>
          <svg
            class="faq-icon"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
          >
            <polyline points="6,9 12,15 18,9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="faq-answer-content">
            <p>
              Absolutely! We provide a 7-day free trial with full access to all features. No credit
              card required to start. Our team will also provide a personal demo and assist with
              initial setup. After the trial, you can choose the plan that suits your needs or
              consult for a custom solution.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- <div class="faq-item fade-in delay-11">
        <button class="faq-question" aria-expanded="false">
          <span>Does QIFESS support multiple languages and currencies?</span>
          <svg
            class="faq-icon"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
          >
            <polyline points="6,9 12,15 18,9"></polyline>
          </svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer">
          <div class="faq-answer-content">
            <p>
              Yes, QIFESS supports both Indonesian and English as interface languages. For
